========= 8.0.0.035 (beta-testing) =========

add(node-tracking): Ability to disable/enable mesonet information gathering from node-tracking.

update(documentation): Improved documentation
update(node-tracking): `pin_by_name` is no longer case sensitive
update(node-tracking): Lon/Lat checks are now implemented to prevent tracking spam for stationary nodes.

refactor(node-tracking): refactored node tracking for better maintainability by adding a string reference `tracking_node_message` 